                p The »<abbr title="/ˈbɪvrɒst/")Bifrost</abbr>« — or »The swaying road to Heaven« — is the legendary Bridge, which connects the heavenly world to the earthly world. The three-rays Rainbowbridge is guarded by the God <abbr title="/ˈheɪmdɑːl/")Heimdall</abbr>. Furthermore, there is red fire burning on the bridge, keeping the »Evil« — until <abbr title="/ˈræɡnəˌrɒk/")Ragnarök</abbr> — from crossing the bridge.

                p.quote »Aber so stark sie auch ist, so wird sie doch zerbrechen, wenn Muspels Söhne kommen, darüber zu reiten.«<abbr title="Gylfaginning 13")&nbsp;<sup class="Kommentar")[1]</sup></abbr>
